index_terms: DEPARTMENT OF HOUSING AND URBAN DEVELOPMENT
summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the condemnation proceedings to acquire certain property in Block 63, A. A. Denny's 5th Addition to The City of Seattle for park, recreation and general corporate purposes under Ordinance 100118; accepting a condemnation award in connection therewith and making a reimbursable appropriation from the Park Acquisition and Development Fund and an appropriation from the Central Freeway Municipal Garage Improvement Fund 1972 therefor.
